Dialogue: 0,1:27:45.04,1:27:48.17,Default,,0,0,0,,凯撒死了
Dialogue: 0,1:27:53.39,1:27:55.89,Default,,0,0,0,,猿类听从...
Dialogue: 0,1:27:56.64,1:27:59.06,Default,,0,0,0,,科巴的命令
Dialogue: 0,1:28:20.29,1:28:22.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我的天哪 快看 城里着火了
Dialogue: 0,1:28:22.66,1:28:24.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我们还能去哪儿呢
Dialogue: 0,1:28:24.75,1:28:26.63,Default,,0,0,0,,凯撒 怎么？
Dialogue: 0,1:28:35.14,1:28:37.14,Default,,0,0,0,,是这儿吗 快到了吗
Dialogue: 0,1:28:37.43,1:28:38.77,Default,,0,0,0,,他要带我们去哪儿
Dialogue: 0,1:28:41.77,1:28:42.65,Default,,0,0,0,,马尔科姆 停车
Dialogue: 0,1:28:51.11,1:28:54.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我不明白 来这儿干嘛
Dialogue: 0,1:28:54.53,1:28:55.58,Default,,0,0,0,,这不重要
Dialogue: 0,1:28:55.61,1:28:58.53,Default,,0,0,0,,现在得躲起来 直到我们弄清城里的情况
Dialogue: 0,1:29:03.12,1:29:04.70,Default,,0,0,0,,把茶几推开
Dialogue: 0,1:29:08.46,1:29:10.84,Default,,0,0,0,,好的 就这儿
Dialogue: 0,1:29:11.96,1:29:12.96,Default,,0,0,0,,好了
Dialogue: 0,1:29:17.80,1:29:18.63,Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸 看
Dialogue: 0,1:29:20.68,1:29:21.84,Default,,0,0,0,,你看
Dialogue: 0,1:29:27.56,1:29:29.89,Default,,0,0,0,,要做手术 可我什么都没有
Dialogue: 0,1:29:31.02,1:29:32.77,Default,,0,0,0,,我住的地方有手术箱 可那儿...
Dialogue: 0,1:29:32.82,1:29:33.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我去吧
Dialogue: 0,1:29:36.20,1:29:37.24,Default,,0,0,0,,那儿不安全
Dialogue: 0,1:29:37.28,1:29:40.20,Default,,0,0,0,,只有他能阻止事态的发展
Dialogue: 0,1:29:42.66,1:29:44.37,Default,,0,0,0,,人类
Dialogue: 0,1:29:44.71,1:29:48.42,Default,,0,0,0,,你们成了猿类的囚犯
Dialogue: 0,1:29:48.46,1:29:52.30,Default,,0,0,0,,你们来尝尝牢笼的滋味
Dialogue: 0,1:29:53.51,1:29:56.01,Default,,0,0,0,,很多人类还没抓到
Dialogue: 0,1:29:56.72,1:29:59.31,Default,,0,0,0,,去 抓住他们
Dialogue: 0,1:31:52.79,1:31:53.87,Default,,0,0,0,,见鬼
Dialogue: 0,1:33:04.07,1:33:05.61,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿 等等
Dialogue: 0,1:33:07.03,1:33:08.49,Default,,0,0,0,,你父亲
Dialogue: 0,1:33:11.29,1:33:13.29,Default,,0,0,0,,他还活着
Dialogue: 0,1:33:25.59,1:33:26.55,Default,,0,0,0,,拿到了
Dialogue: 0,1:33:27.05,1:33:28.26,Default,,0,0,0,,他怎么样
Dialogue: 0,1:33:53.16,1:33:55.95,Default,,0,0,0,,你的 母亲
Dialogue: 0,1:33:58.46,1:33:59.84,Default,,0,0,0,,弟弟
Dialogue: 0,1:34:01.00,1:34:02.33,Default,,0,0,0,,安全吗
Dialogue: 0,1:34:14.31,1:34:15.36,Default,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,1:34:15.77,1:34:16.90,Default,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,1:34:20.11,1:34:22.57,Default,,0,0,0,,不是人类
Dialogue: 0,1:34:26.82,1:34:28.41,Default,,0,0,0,,是科巴
Dialogue: 0,1:34:32.28,1:34:33.24,Default,,0,0,0,,马尔科姆
Dialogue: 0,1:34:33.99,1:34:35.45,Default,,0,0,0,,对 没错
Dialogue: 0,1:34:37.12,1:34:38.45,Default,,0,0,0,,凯撒
Dialogue: 0,1:34:40.13,1:34:42.26,Default,,0,0,0,,现在需要做手术了
Dialogue: 0,1:34:46.26,1:34:47.76,Default,,0,0,0,,儿子
Dialogue: 0,1:35:22.54,1:35:24.21,Default,,0,0,0,,他怎么样
Dialogue: 0,1:35:26.51,1:35:28.05,Default,,0,0,0,,还得观察
Dialogue: 0,1:35:29.55,1:35:31.56,Default,,0,0,0,,他很强壮
Dialogue: 0,1:35:40.98,1:35:42.98,Default,,0,0,0,,他不会有事的
Dialogue: 0,1:36:22.35,1:36:23.85,Default,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,1:36:27.65,1:36:29.36,Default,,0,0,0,,这...
Dialogue: 0,1:36:29.69,1:36:31.06,Default,,0,0,0,,是我的错
Dialogue: 0,1:36:33.53,1:36:35.74,Default,,0,0,0,,是科巴背叛了你
Dialogue: 0,1:36:36.07,1:36:37.49,Default,,0,0,0,,是我...
Dialogue: 0,1:36:37.53,1:36:41.16,Default,,0,0,0,,去选择相信他...
Dialogue: 0,1:36:41.83,1:36:45.92,Default,,0,0,0,,只因为他是猿类
Dialogue: 0,1:36:47.09,1:36:49.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我总是觉得...
Dialogue: 0,1:36:50.01,1:36:53.89,Default,,0,0,0,,猿类好过人类
Dialogue: 0,1:36:56.18,1:36:58.27,Default,,0,0,0,,现在才明白...
Dialogue: 0,1:37:00.06,1:37:04.44,Default,,0,0,0,,原来我们如此相似
Dialogue: 0,1:37:08.94,1:37:11.27,Default,,0,0,0,,科巴现在在哪儿
Dialogue: 0,1:37:18.95,1:37:22.41,Default,,0,0,0,,那些不愿跟着他的呢？
Dialogue: 0,1:37:53.65,1:37:55.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我虚弱时可不一定
Dialogue: 0,1:37:58.32,1:38:02.61,Default,,0,0,0,,猿类总是追随最强者
Dialogue: 0,1:38:05.75,1:38:09.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我必须设法阻止他
Dialogue: 0,1:38:19.80,1:38:21.51,Default,,0,0,0,,父亲
Dialogue: 0,1:38:24.18,1:38:28.14,Default,,0,0,0,,让我来帮你
Dialogue: 0,1:39:19.36,1:39:21.40,Default,,0,0,0,,求你了 放我们走吧
Dialogue: 0,1:41:41.09,1:41:42.22,Default,,0,0,0,,好了
Dialogue: 0,1:41:42.26,1:41:44.14,Default,,0,0,0,,凯撒 你看
Dialogue: 0,1:41:45.05,1:41:46.26,Default,,0,0,0,,苹果
Dialogue: 0,1:41:46.93,1:41:48.06,Default,,0,0,0,,苹果
Dialogue: 0,1:41:48.47,1:41:50.39,Default,,0,0,0,,很好
Dialogue: 0,1:41:51.22,1:41:52.39,Default,,0,0,0,,家
Dialogue: 0,1:41:53.10,1:41:54.48,Default,,0,0,0,,家
Dialogue: 0,1:41:56.60,1:41:57.97,Default,,0,0,0,,家
Dialogue: 0,1:41:59.73,1:42:00.81,Default,,0,0,0,,对了
Dialogue: 0,1:42:02.73,1:42:04.61,Default,,0,0,0,,这是你的家
Dialogue: 0,1:42:05.11,1:42:06.57,Default,,0,0,0,,你的家
Dialogue: 0,1:42:08.99,1:42:10.82,Default,,0,0,0,,很好 很好
Dialogue: 0,1:42:11.83,1:42:13.42,Default,,0,0,0,,非常好
Dialogue: 0,1:42:36.48,1:42:38.11,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,1:42:38.15,1:42:40.28,Default,,0,0,0,,其实我不想打扰你
Dialogue: 0,1:42:44.28,1:42:46.66,Default,,0,0,0,,已经过去两天了
Dialogue: 0,1:42:52.74,1:42:54.91,Default,,0,0,0,,你儿子还没回来吗
Dialogue: 0,1:42:59.92,1:43:01.88,Default,,0,0,0,,那人是谁
Dialogue: 0,1:43:03.30,1:43:04.93,Default,,0,0,0,,录像里的
Dialogue: 0,1:43:07.67,1:43:11.01,Default,,0,0,0,,一个好人
Dialogue: 0,1:43:13.89,1:43:16.23,Default,,0,0,0,,就像你
Dialogue: 0,1:43:47.05,1:43:49.01,Default,,0,0,0,,我带他们走地铁进入塔楼
Dialogue: 0,1:43:49.05,1:43:51.01,Default,,0,0,0,,这样他们就不会被发现
Dialogue: 0,1:43:51.80,1:43:52.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我爱你
Dialogue: 0,1:44:02.65,1:44:04.90,Default,,0,0,0,,必须出发 快
Dialogue: 0,1:44:16.20,1:44:17.36,Default,,0,0,0,,你还好吗
Dialogue: 0,1:44:28.17,1:44:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,谁在那儿
Dialogue: 0,1:44:30.17,1:44:32.55,Default,,0,0,0,,如果是人类 最好喊一声
Dialogue: 0,1:44:32.59,1:44:34.55,Default,,0,0,0,,是我 马尔科姆
Dialogue: 0,1:44:34.59,1:44:35.88,Default,,0,0,0,,不要开枪
Dialogue: 0,1:44:37.97,1:44:39.34,Default,,0,0,0,,就走这边的楼梯
Dialogue: 0,1:44:39.39,1:44:41.64,Default,,0,0,0,,从地下迂回上去 明白吗
Dialogue: 0,1:44:41.69,1:44:42.73,Default,,0,0,0,,走
Dialogue: 0,1:44:46.82,1:44:47.78,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,1:44:48.57,1:44:50.41,Default,,0,0,0,,信任
Dialogue: 0,1:44:57.45,1:44:59.49,Default,,0,0,0,,好 我要出来了
Dialogue: 0,1:44:59.54,1:45:01.25,Default,,0,0,0,,别开枪
Dialogue: 0,1:45:19.06,1:45:20.44,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿
Dialogue: 0,1:45:20.47,1:45:22.01,Default,,0,0,0,,瞧我找到谁了
Dialogue: 0,1:45:22.06,1:45:24.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我都不知道你逃出来了
Dialogue: 0,1:45:24.31,1:45:25.47,Default,,0,0,0,,见到你真好
Dialogue: 0,1:45:25.52,1:45:27.06,Default,,0,0,0,,别担心
Dialogue: 0,1:45:27.11,1:45:28.78,Default,,0,0,0,,马上就能翻盘了
Dialogue: 0,1:45:28.82,1:45:30.74,Default,,0,0,0,,什么意思 发生什么了
Dialogue: 0,1:45:30.78,1:45:32.62,Default,,0,0,0,,那些猿类 都聚在塔楼上
Dialogue: 0,1:45:32.65,1:45:34.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我失去信号了 等等
Dialogue: 0,1:45:34.57,1:45:35.65,Default,,0,0,0,,继续试
Dialogue: 0,1:45:35.70,1:45:37.20,Default,,0,0,0,,马尔科姆 你来看
Dialogue: 0,1:45:38.58,1:45:41.83,Default,,0,0,0,,炸药 五磅一组
Dialogue: 0,1:45:42.45,1:45:44.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我们刚刚开始设置
Dialogue: 0,1:45:44.75,1:45:47.21,Default,,0,0,0,,靠它们把整座塔炸塌
Dialogue: 0,1:45:49.42,1:45:51.76,Default,,0,0,0,,把他们一锅端了
Dialogue: 0,1:45:52.34,1:45:54.26,Default,,0,0,0,,你也来帮忙吧
Dialogue: 0,1:46:32.80,1:46:36.18,Default,,0,0,0,,这里是旧金山 正在尝试联络 如果接受到讯息
Dialogue: 0,1:46:36.22,1:46:39.31,Default,,0,0,0,,请表明你的身份和位置 完毕
Dialogue: 0,1:46:43.39,1:46:45.31,Default,,0,0,0,,好了 来吧
Dialogue: 0,1:46:45.35,1:46:47.31,Default,,0,0,0,,如果能接受到这条讯息
Dialogue: 0,1:46:47.36,1:46:49.81,Default,,0,0,0,,请表明你的身份和位置 完毕
Dialogue: 0,1:46:58.24,1:46:59.54,Default,,0,0,0,,这里是旧金山...
Dialogue: 0,1:46:59.57,1:47:01.95,Default,,0,0,0,,正在尝试联络 如果收到讯息
Dialogue: 0,1:47:01.99,1:47:04.86,Default,,0,0,0,,请表明你的身份和位置 完毕
Dialogue: 0,1:47:07.41,1:47:09.37,Default,,0,0,0,,- 嘿  - 嘿
Dialogue: 0,1:47:16.72,1:47:19.64,Default,,0,0,0,,如果收到讯息 请表明你的...
Dialogue: 0,1:47:19.68,1:47:20.97,Default,,0,0,0,,身份和位置 完毕
Dialogue: 0,1:47:25.68,1:47:26.76,Default,,0,0,0,,德雷福斯
Dialogue: 0,1:47:30.98,1:47:32.44,Default,,0,0,0,,- 有人听到吗  - 维尔纳
Dialogue: 0,1:47:35.82,1:47:38.74,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉 我不能让你这么做
Dialogue: 0,1:47:40.03,1:47:41.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我们要给他机会
Dialogue: 0,1:47:42.87,1:47:44.79,Default,,0,0,0,,再给他点时间
Dialogue: 0,1:47:45.49,1:47:47.20,Default,,0,0,0,,他现在在上面
Dialogue: 0,1:47:49.79,1:47:51.63,Default,,0,0,0,,谁在上面？
Dialogue: 0,1:48:28.20,1:48:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,凯撒 这里没你的事
Dialogue: 0,1:48:35.96,1:48:38.00,Default,,0,0,0,,猿类听从...
Dialogue: 0,1:48:39.13,1:48:40.79,Default,,0,0,0,,科巴的
Dialogue: 0,1:48:44.39,1:48:46.85,Default,,0,0,0,,追随科巴...
Dialogue: 0,1:48:47.81,1:48:48.85,Default,,0,0,0,,只有战争
Dialogue: 0,1:48:49.14,1:48:51.72,Default,,0,0,0,,猿类打赢了
Dialogue: 0,1:48:53.35,1:48:56.64,Default,,0,0,0,,猿类团结强大
Dialogue: 0,1:49:01.82,1:49:03.24,Default,,0,0,0,,凯撒
Dialogue: 0,1:49:04.70,1:49:06.04,Default,,0,0,0,,太弱
Dialogue: 0,1:49:09.83,1:49:12.92,Default,,0,0,0,,科巴 更弱
Dialogue: 0,1:50:02.21,1:50:04.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我说 你脑袋进水了吧
Dialogue: 0,1:50:05.55,1:50:08.55,Default,,0,0,0,,不 我亲身经历过 我了解他们的生活
Dialogue: 0,1:50:09.39,1:50:11.39,Default,,0,0,0,,他们和我们一样 要生存
Dialogue: 0,1:50:11.43,1:50:12.68,Default,,0,0,0,,并不想战争
Dialogue: 0,1:50:12.72,1:50:14.35,Default,,0,0,0,,他们是畜生
Dialogue: 0,1:50:14.39,1:50:15.76,Default,,0,0,0,,他们袭击了我们
Dialogue: 0,1:50:15.81,1:50:18.60,Default,,0,0,0,,他们以为我们先攻击的 他们以为他死了 但其实没有...
Dialogue: 0,1:50:18.65,1:50:20.24,Default,,0,0,0,,坐下 芬尼
Dialogue: 0,1:50:20.98,1:50:22.40,Default,,0,0,0,,坐下
Dialogue: 0,1:50:45.76,1:50:47.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我相信科巴 像兄弟一样
Dialogue: 0,1:50:48.18,1:50:51.48,Default,,0,0,0,,凯撒的兄弟是人类
Dialogue: 0,1:50:53.93,1:50:56.60,Default,,0,0,0,,科巴为猿类而战
Dialogue: 0,1:50:56.94,1:50:58.69,Default,,0,0,0,,解放猿类！
Dialogue: 0,1:51:01.27,1:51:02.64,Default,,0,0,0,,还杀了猿类
Dialogue: 0,1:51:02.69,1:51:04.27,Default,,0,0,0,,科巴是为自己而战
Dialogue: 0,1:51:13.12,1:51:14.46,Default,,0,0,0,,科巴
Dialogue: 0,1:51:15.00,1:51:18.71,Default,,0,0,0,,只配关笼子里
Dialogue: 0,1:52:06.84,1:52:08.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道 这听起来很奇怪
Dialogue: 0,1:52:09.01,1:52:10.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我想你根本就没明白
Dialogue: 0,1:52:15.72,1:52:17.76,Default,,0,0,0,,你以为阻止我就有用吗
Dialogue: 0,1:52:18.35,1:52:20.02,Default,,0,0,0,,他们来了
Dialogue: 0,1:52:21.19,1:52:23.61,Default,,0,0,0,,我们刚才跟北部的军事基地联系上了
Dialogue: 0,1:52:24.56,1:52:27.10,Default,,0,0,0,,他们已经在路上了
Dialogue: 0,1:52:27.90,1:52:29.02,Default,,0,0,0,,是真的
Dialogue: 0,1:52:33.95,1:52:34.83,Default,,0,0,0,,德雷福斯
Dialogue: 0,1:52:34.87,1:52:36.37,Default,,0,0,0,,你干什么？
Dialogue: 0,1:52:46.55,1:52:48.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我只想要拯救人类
Dialogue: 0,1:52:48.55,1:52:49.39,Default,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,1:55:10.86,1:55:12.07,Default,,0,0,0,,猿类...
Dialogue: 0,1:55:12.90,1:55:14.86,Default,,0,0,0,,不杀...
Dialogue: 0,1:55:15.74,1:55:17.03,Default,,0,0,0,,猿类
Dialogue: 0,1:55:42.55,1:55:44.76,Default,,0,0,0,,你不是...
Dialogue: 0,1:55:46.56,1:55:48.40,Default,,0,0,0,,猿类
Dialogue: 0,1:55:52.23,1:55:53.81,Default,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,1:57:08.14,1:57:09.65,Default,,0,0,0,,放开他
Dialogue: 0,1:57:27.49,1:57:29.20,Default,,0,0,0,,这儿不安全
Dialogue: 0,1:57:29.83,1:57:32.54,Default,,0,0,0,,他们跟其他人类联系上了 是军队
Dialogue: 0,1:57:33.12,1:57:35.16,Default,,0,0,0,,你们快走吧 全都走
Dialogue: 0,1:57:36.17,1:57:39.84,Default,,0,0,0,,如果现在不走 将面临全面战争
Dialogue: 0,1:57:39.88,1:57:41.64,Default,,0,0,0,,战争...
Dialogue: 0,1:57:41.67,1:57:43.80,Default,,0,0,0,,早就已经..
Dialogue: 0,1:57:44.89,1:57:46.02,Default,,0,0,0,,开始
Dialogue: 0,1:57:48.01,1:57:50.76,Default,,0,0,0,,猿类挑起的战争
Dialogue: 0,1:57:53.89,1:57:55.60,Default,,0,0,0,,而人类...
Dialogue: 0,1:57:58.02,1:58:01.06,Default,,0,0,0,,人类绝不会原谅
Dialogue: 0,1:58:04.28,1:58:08.04,Default,,0,0,0,,你们先走
Dialogue: 0,1:58:08.37,1:58:12.08,Default,,0,0,0,,别等到战斗开始
Dialogue: 0,1:58:13.91,1:58:15.70,Default,,0,0,0,,非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,1:58:18.21,1:58:21.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我的朋友
Dialogue: 0,1:58:25.88,1:58:28.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我曾以为我们还有机会
Dialogue: 0,1:58:32.14,1:58:34.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我也曾以为
